data.description:
No agents involved. This is a private sale. Call Michael at 801-803-4314. $265,000 or best offer.

For Sale 3 bedroom 2 bath, granite countertops, tile floors, tile backsplash in the kitchen, dark wood cabinets, tile shower, recessed lighting in the whole house, 2 sinks in master bathroom, gas fireplace outlined in tile, expensive stainless steel french door refrigerator, 2 car fully painted garage, complete fenced backyard with sprinklers and shed, and landscaped front yard. This is a private sale do not call agents that zillow has listed on this ad. Call Michael at 801-803-4314
